        <span>Patients and family members in the area for care at Ashley Regional or other Vernal-area medical facilities.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hcard">
        <div class="hc-icon">🦕</div>
        <strong>Adventure Travelers</strong>
        <span>Using Naples as a launch point for Dinosaur National Monument, Flaming Gorge, and the surrounding canyon country.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hcard">
        <div class="hc-icon">⛽</div>
        <strong>Oilfield &amp; Energy Crews</strong>
        <span>Workers on rotating assignments throughout Uintah County including the Naples area. Weekly and monthly crew rates available.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hcard">
        <div class="hc-icon">🏛️</div>
        <strong>Government &amp; Per Diem</strong>
        <span>County, state, and federal employees on assignment in the Uintah Basin. Per diem friendly with itemized receipts provided.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section rv">
    <h2>What You Get at Best Western Vernal</h2>
    <p>A full-service hotel experience — not a budget motel or a bare-bones extended stay property. Every room includes the same complete amenity set whether you're here for one night or three months.</p>
