      <p><strong>Call for current rates:</strong> Weekly and monthly pricing varies by season and room type. Call or text us directly at <a href="tel:4357896625">(435) 789-6625</a> — extended stay rates are often not accurately listed on third-party booking sites.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</div><!-- /content-wrap -->

