        <h2>Naples, Utah Hotel FAQ</h2>
        <div class="gline"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Is there a hotel in Naples, Utah? <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button><div class="faq-a"><p>Naples, Utah does not have a full-service hotel within its city limits. The closest hotel isBest Western Vernal Inn, located just minutes away in neighboring Vernal. The two cities share a border and are functionally a single community — the drive between them is brief.</p></div></div>
